snippet.textDisplay:
Mein hu ke dukho se picha chudane ki koshish karta 
Apni uljhano ne se sulajhne ki koshish karta hu
Mohabbat na ho is baat ki koshish karta hu 
Mohabbat se dur jane ki koshish karta hu
Yani kya! Mein use bhul jane ki koshish karta hu
Yani koi na mumkin si koshish karta hu 
Har pehar uski yaad mujhe rulane ki koshish karti hai
Har baat uski dil dukhane ki koshish karti hai
Dekh kar uski tasveer apni ankhon ko aziyat se bachane ki koshish karta hu 
Jagu to uske khyal se or soou to uske khawab se bachne ki koshish karta hu 
Soch ta hu koshish karlu usse mukammal bhul jane ki 
Magar mein bhi ahmak hu namumkin ki koshish karta hu
